OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774094594
OL,3,CFirst female Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,4,Cinstallation to host 2,000 guests
OL,6,FMore than two thousand people from
OL,7,Facross the country and around the
OL,8,Fworld will attend the Installation of
OL,9,Fthe first female Archbishop of
OL,10,FCanterbury next week.
OL,12,FDame Sarah Mullally, who is walking a
OL,13,F140km ancient pilgrim route from
OL,14,FLondon to Canterbury Cathedral in
OL,15,Fpreparation for her Installation, said
OL,16,Fthe theme of pilgrimage will be
OL,17,Freflected in the service on Wednesday
OL,18,F25 March.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
